<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-B0vP5xmATw1+K9KRQjQERJvTumQW0nPEzvF6L/Z6nronJ3oUOFUFpCjEUQouq2+l" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.7.2/css/all.css">
  <title>Data Declaration Form</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }

    .container {
      width: 210mm;
      /* Set width to A4 width */
      margin: 0 auto;
      /* Center the container horizontally */
      padding: 20mm;
      /* Adjusted padding for content */
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: none;
      /* Remove the border-bottom */
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-left: 30px;
      /* Adjusted padding */
      position: relative;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    ul li:before {
      content: "â€¢";
      position: absolute;
      left: 15px;
      /* Adjusted position */
    }

    .signature {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ff7f0d;
    }

    .contact-details {
      margin-left: 5px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      border-left: 1px solid #ff7f0d;
    }

    .signature p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .orange-line {
      height: 10px;
      background-color: #ff7f0d;
      /* Orange color */
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      /* Adjust margin as needed */
    }

    .contact-icons {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-icons img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }

    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .logo-container img {
      width: 45%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .contact-info img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .contact-details {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .contact-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .signature p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      text-align: left;
      /* Align text to the left */
    }

    .signature p {
      /* border-bottom: 1px solid #000000; */
      /* Add red underscore */
      width: 300px;
      /* Set width to control the length of the underscore */
      display: block;
      /* Make span behave like a block element */
    }

    .underscore {
      border-bottom: 1px solid black;
      padding: 0 5px;
      /* Optional: adjust padding as needed */
      display: inline-block;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      /* Ensures the underscore line spans the width of the content */
    }

    .wide {
      width: 200px;
      /* Adjust the width as needed */
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <img src="<%= data.BACKEND_URL %>/gs1Images/backend/logo/service_default_image.jpeg" alt="logo"
        style="width: 250px; height: 100px; object-fit: contain;">
      <img src="<%= data.BACKEND_URL %>/gs1Images/backend/logo/logo.png"
        style="width: 250px; height: 100px; object-fit: contain;">
    </div>
    <div class="header">
      <div class="orange-line"></div>
    </div>
    <p>I, <span class="underscore wide"> <Strong>
          <%= data.memberData.membername %>
        </Strong> </span>, hereby declare and affirm that I understand and acknowledge the following regarding the
      products data or information that I create or add, as part of the migration process by GS1:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Accuracy of Data:</strong> I understand that it is my responsibility to ensure the accuracy and
        integrity of
        the products data that I create or add during the migration process. I will diligently verify and
        cross-reference all relevant information to ensure its correctness and completeness.</li>
      <li><strong>Duplication of Products:</strong> I affirm that I will take all necessary measures to prevent the
        duplication of any product within the database. I will thoroughly review existing data and crosscheck any new
        additions to avoid redundant entries.</li>
      <li><strong>Data Maintenance:</strong> I acknowledge that the responsibility for maintaining the accuracy and
        consistency of the products data rests with me. I will promptly address any identified errors,
        discrepancies, or outdated information, and take appropriate action to rectify them.</li>
      <li><strong>Compliance with GS1 Guidelines:</strong> I understand that the migration process follows the GS1
        guidelines and standards. I will adhere to these guidelines, ensuring that the data structure,
        attributes, and formats align with the specified requirements.</li>
      <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> I affirm that the products data or information I create or add complies
        with all
        applicable laws, regulations, and industry standards. I will not include any misleading, inaccurate,
        or deceptive information.</li>
      <li><strong>Confidentiality and Data Protection:</strong> I acknowledge the confidential nature of the products
        data
        and commit to safeguarding its confidentiality and integrity. I will handle the data responsibly
        and take necessary precautions to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.</li>
      <li><strong>Collaboration and Communication:</strong> I understand the importance of collaboration and effective
        communication within the migration process. I will actively engage with other team members,
        stakeholders, and GS1 representatives to address any data-related concerns, seek clarifications,
        and ensure a smooth transition.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>By signing below, I confirm that I have read and understood this Data Declaration. I acknowledge that I
      am fully responsible for the accuracy, non-duplication, selection of right category, and maintenance of
      the products data that I create or add during the GS1 migration process,</p>
    <div class="signaturessd">
      <div class="flex" style="display: flex;">
        <p style="width: 80px;">Signature:</p>
         <p style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;width: 200px;"></p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex" style="display: flex;">
        <p style="width: 80px;">Date:
        </p>
         <p style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;width: 200px;"> <%= data.memberData.date %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex" style="display: flex;">
        <p style="width: 80px;">Name:
        </p>
         <p style="border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;width: 200px;"> <%= data.memberData.membername %></p>
      </div>
      <hr style="border-color: #ff7f0d;">
      
    </div>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <img src="<%= data.memberData.qrcode %>" alt="Screenshot-2024-04-23-154519" alt="Phone"
        style="width: 150px; height: 100px; object-fit: contain;">
      <div class="contact-details">
        <p><i class="fas fa-phone" style="margin-right: 10px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>+966-11-218-2423</p>
        <p><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="margin-right: 10px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>gs1sa@gs1.org.sa</p>
        <p>King Fahad Branch Road, AlMoatamarat Dist. P.O.Box 16683 Riyadh 11474, Saudi Arabia</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>